{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/lowongan-kerja-remote-atau-magang-jadi-jurnalis-dan-blogger/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Lowongan Kerja Remote atau Magang Jadi Jurnalis dan Blogger!","content":"<p>Hallo!</p>\n<p>Suka manga tapi ngga bisa gambar? Suka film tapi ngga bisa akting?</p>\n<p>Hobi main <em>game</em> tapi ngga bisa main <em>game</em> karena alasan tertentu?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3006\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3006\" data-attachment-id=\"3006\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lowongan-kerja-remote-atau-magang-jadi-jurnalis-dan-blogger/attachment/body2-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Team Starwars atau Team Gundam\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3006\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3006\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jangan khawatir! <em>Fear no more</em>! Sekarang Kamu bisa menulis tentang <em>pop culture</em> (komik, <em>game, </em>film animasi), dan segala sesuatu yang berhubungan dengannya di CIAYO Blog. Selain tulisan dimuat, Kamu juga dapet eksposur karena nama dan foto <em>author </em>akan ditampilkan. Kami tidak membatasi gaya penulisan. Kamu boleh bebas menulis dengan sopan dan juga tidak mengandung SARA atau pornografi.</p>\n<p>Tulisan yang menarik dan terpilih juga berkesempatan untuk dijadikan <em>headline news</em> serta diposting di akun media sosial CIAYO Comics yang merupakan situs komik online gratis. Setiap artikel yang lolos kurasi dan dimuat, akan mendapatkan <em>reward </em>per artikel.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_377\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-377\" data-attachment-id=\"377\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/coma-event-wadah-bagi-pecinta-komik-dan-pop-culture/attachment/coma1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Coma1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tim CIAYO Comics ngobrol-ngobrol dengan pengunjung COMA Event (Dokumentasi CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-377\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1.jpg\" alt=\"Tim CIAYO Comics ngobrol-ngobrol dengan pengunjung COMA Event (Dokumentasi CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Coma1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-377\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">COMA Event (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tulisan bisa membahas tentang: review komik manga, review komik one shot, review film animasi atau film box office hollywood, review game, cerita pengalaman atau hasil liputan Kamu di <em>event-event pop culture </em>atau di negeri orang, tulisan <em>unboxing game console</em>, komik ataupun mainan seperti gundam, <em>action figure</em> dan lain sebagainya. Pokoknya jangan takut untuk berekspresi dan bereksperimen dalam tulisan kamu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3009\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3009\" data-attachment-id=\"3009\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lowongan-kerja-remote-atau-magang-jadi-jurnalis-dan-blogger/attachment/body1-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fear no more!\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3009\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5.jpg\" alt=\"Fear no more! (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body1-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3009\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fear no more! (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kami sangat menganjurkan untuk melampirkan gambar dengan format jpeg dan lampiran video dengan format link youtube di artikelmu. Gambar dan video yang diambil boleh menggunakan kamera ponsel beresolusi tinggi ataupun kamera DSLR.</p>\n<p>Oh yah, <em>one more thing</em>: artikel yang dikirim harus asli yah, jangan main <em>copy paste</em> punya orang lain, nanti dimarahin lho!</p>\n<p>Ayo, tunggu apalagi?</p>\n<p>Segera kirimkan tulisanmu ke <a href=\"mailto:hallo@ciayo.com\">hallo@ciayo.com</a> <em>so that the world can hear and know you</em>!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"9cb23345-3e6a-5394-8363-ffd2eca856a7"}}}